  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to evaluate leakage of a newly developed ostomy product compared
      to standard care in subjects with colostomies. Subjects will be asked to use each test
      product for 2 weeks - in total, the study period is 4 weeks and the hypothesis is to show
      that the newly developed ostomy product is significantly better to reduce leakage compared to
      standard care.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
